    "truncated_body_text": "In my previous posts, you encountered the concepts of \"fair play\" or \"fair bet.\" In this post, I’m going to introduce this concept in more detail, as it is one of the fundamental principles of option pricing and a key concept in risk management. I will also introduce a bet sizing mathematical model known as the Kelly criterion.",
